CYRUSERV Community Jabber!

This is the CYRUSERV Community Jabber server. This is an Onion based server, clearnet jabber servers will not know how to find it. This server permits registration, so anyone can use it. It is a community service provided by Occulus Omega for your convenience.

My username is occuomega@cyjabr4pfzupo7pg.onion if you want to contact me. My OTR fingerprint is: F28DFC87 52B4FCDD B50C7C27 3106CEAB BEFF5125.

Cyrus goes by cyrus@cyjabr4pfzupo7pg.onion and uses the OTR fingerprint: 07A8AA5F 569D70F0 50B5C85C D4DA314E DC3C8654.

Server now supports SSL. Server can communicate with other Onion servers.

Please donate some Bitcoin: 1EV95pVv2gZYLcZEnHRtmLL4Dh8k878Lz4

To access this service your client needs...

  • Use encryption if available (the option between use/don't use encryption).
  • Plaintext authentication.
  • DNS lookups through proxy.
  • Register an account first.

gajim: This client works fine for me and seems to have options for Tor now. Though, I use it behind a Anonymizing Middlebox. If you can't figure it out do not ask me, ask the internet.

I hope you enjoy the service!
